entity.subject: Your Order Confirmation ✅
entity.template:
Subject: Your Order Confirmation - Thank You for Shopping with Us!


Dear {{ buyer.name }},

Thank you for your recent purchase from {{ company.name }}! We are excited to confirm that your order has been successfully placed. Below are the details of your order:

Order Number: {{ order.id }}

Order Date: {{ order.createdDate }}


Items Purchased:

  1. [Product Name 1]
  • Quantity: [Quantity]
  • Price: [Price]
  1. [Product Name 2]
  • Quantity: [Quantity]
  • Price: [Price]
  1. [Product Name 3]
  • Quantity: [Quantity]
  • Price: [Price]


Shipping Information:

  • Shipping Address: [Customer's Shipping Address]
  • Shipping Method: [Shipping Method]
  • Estimated Delivery Date: [Estimated Delivery Date]

Billing Information:

  • Billing Address: [Customer's Billing Address]
  • Payment Method: [Payment Method]

You can track your order and view your purchase history by logging into your account on our website [Your Website URL].

If you have any questions or need further assistance, please do not hesitate to contact our customer service team at [Customer Service Email] or [Customer Service Phone Number].

Thank you for choosing [Your Company Name]. We hope you enjoy your new products!

Best regards,

[Your Name]

[Your Position]

[Your Company Name]

[Your Contact Information]
